{"tid":259536,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂開始對修改過系統的3DS進行大範圍ban機","createTime":"2017-05-27T04:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T08:52:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f241de86a68dfc54053f7d0c13b2b0b6c4547d7","tid":259536,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"2017/05/27 03:54<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在Sighax發佈之後，3DS宣告全版本被開放，任何型號任何系統版本，都能安裝自制系統。<br />\n但是從5月25日開始，陸續有大量3DS玩家報告自己的機器被ban，錯誤代碼是002-0102<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這次ban的機制是：<br />\n並不清楚任天堂的這次的檢測機制，但是這次被ban掉的都是裝有自制系統的3DS。與之前運行洩漏版口袋怪獸被ban不同的是，這次波及的範圍並不是運行了特定偷跑的遊戲，而是針對安裝了自制系統的3DS硬件本身。<br />\n<br />\n如果我被ban了，那意味著什麼？<br />\n意味著你除了還能正常登陸eshop購買遊戲之外（因為任天堂仍然想要你的錢），其他與網絡關聯的事情都不能進行，例如網絡聯機對戰或者數據交換。<br />\n<br />\n如果安裝了自制系統，怎麼避免被ban？<br />\n關掉Wifi開關，3DS不要聯網。然後靜觀其變<br />\n<br />\n還會有後續的ban機潮嗎？<br />\n目前不清楚會不會後續持續ban機，靜觀其變<br />\n<br />\n這次是只針對Sighax安裝的自制系統嗎？<br />\n不是，用MenuHax、Arm9LoadHax、Boot9Hax&hellip;&hellip;等等都受到了波及<br />\n<br />\n是只針對使用了Freeshop的用戶嗎？<br />\n不是，即使從未使用Freeshop的玩家，這次也有不少被ban"},{"pid":"a9f71b8d1f9e553ab94f277828bf0b92f00bae6e","tid":259536,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"ban的主要原因已經確定是黑店freeshop了，有勇者拿剛破解的幾台機器做實驗，不管你什麼區域，只要用freeshop就會被秒ban，如果你還在意你的3ds的話，現在就卸載freeshop，這軟件已經觸及了任天堂容忍的底線了"},{"pid":"a537f9153f2f88541e68e9fb3e11b8ac3d94b665","tid":259536,"uid":105822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"唔係直接將部機變磚已經好好了"},{"pid":"414f58bd31e42bca8db3f784d8e05becbe890cb3","tid":259536,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1bb398e5a23b986fb94cd94d12aeea921824e8","tid":259536,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:30:28.000Z","msg":"家陣二手買唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec84e445a530960c833dff68b668833d4f98e50","tid":259536,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae9af28fb3fb780325b3ced2cfbe36f7c3a7709","tid":259536,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:40:52.000Z","msg":"任地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02289e260e7414ac7bb6f598bc784482ede8c0a7","tid":259536,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T08:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}